 />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2330878\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2330878</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n19號<br />\n派文宣慘遭強國男劏肚割頸，中六學生永久斷兩頸肌；60歲施被控襲警，被扑頭流血，判監一個月上訴<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2331601\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2331601</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n20號<br />\n13歲伍同學，沒有反抗下遭警甴以膝頭壓頭，太陽穴受傷；將軍澳支那死賤畜用刀狂斬連儂牆寶寶，寶寶受重傷<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2333011\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2333011</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"df6ff1bc72f2249bd49141ba849921e8c95ab3df","tid":2333011,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:36:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4d7252e377748a89bf82aa6c17b7cfbff402ebc6","tid":2333011,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:39:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02f7fb77a7b189aa60eafd96d83632386337ce16","tid":2333011,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:39:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3461b402b08236f6383b3ec99e7334c7c2761bf","tid":2333011,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:40:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b367ee56d5b29ff8ee0c74c745736c831b02eeb","tid":2333011,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:40:52.000Z","msg":"係咪自推反而會沉底...<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f73c7eeb8372183124f850d43755cbb9480dfb0","tid":2333011,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-20T05:41:57.000Z","msg":"820：將軍澳遊蕩跟蹤